Local models (recommended, not distributed):

- Ziqpu's local-model benchmark (crates/model) recommends and, only at the user's request, points
  the user's own llama.cpp runtime at open-weight models on the Hugging Face Hub (e.g. Llama 3.2 —
  Meta Llama Community License; GPT-OSS — Apache-2.0; Qwen — Apache-2.0 or the Qwen license). Ziqpu
  does not fetch, bundle, or redistribute any model weights; each model is downloaded by, and
  governed by its own license accepted by, the user at download time. No model license attaches to
  Ziqpu's own source.

